{"tid":2139344,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"身體組成研究社","createTime":"2020-08-04T08:23:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T09:36:31.000Z","uid":144768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1711af912133f0a4835e9f2bad6013dca5e023cf","tid":2139344,"uid":144768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T08:23:28.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇咗下面條片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3JSQKoL2YpM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3JSQKoL2YpM&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4YdzUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=2e56d6a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3JSQKoL2YpM</a><br />\n<br />\n片中老爸聲稱減完嘅數字係如下圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sxHfhtt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsxHfhtt.png&h=97b151f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好奇幫佢計一計：<br />\n體重56.4kg，當中12.8%體脂，即體脂重7.2kg<br />\n加上骨骼肌重27.6，咁水份重=56.4-27.6-7.2=21.6kg<br />\n咁水份咪只佔人體21.6/56.4=38%<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n合理咩？<br />\n定我理解有錯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abcc7a92ca07b994b69f5e02aaa2fad8de47c57f","tid":2139344,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T08:24:39.000Z","msg":"人體鍊成係鍊金術禁忌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7fbcb70d1deccad4a4fd13f883cb156e5f4bb94","tid":2139344,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T08:46:50.000Z","msg":"其實點樣分開計d骨重量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3678d46ebaacf21d0ba36aa821981235ba5fe6e","tid":2139344,"uid":144768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7fbcb70d1deccad4a4fd13f883cb156e5f4bb94","tid":2139344,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score